Introduction:
{{Indrop=1;Outdrop=1}}
Headache Diagnosis helps determine the cause of headaches in adults. It includes diseases that cause headache as an early or prominent symptom. It does not address pain that is felt primarily in the eye, ear, nose, mouth, or jaw.

